                            <div class="fl rec2_zfbBox">
                                <img src="/images/yh/alipay.jpg"/>
                            </div>
                            <div class="fl rec2_zfbBoxText">支付宝转账（手机转账0手续费）</div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="rec2_FormBox ">
                            <div class="rec2_Title fl">
                                支付宝账号：
                            </div>
                            <div class="rec2_FomeContent fl">
                                <input type="text" class="inputText" ng-model="vm.alipay_account" placeholder="请输入支付宝账户" required autofocus>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="rec2_FormBox ">
                            <div class="rec2_Title fl">
                                支付宝姓名：
                            </div>
                            <div class="rec2_FomeContent fl">
                                <input type="text" class="inputText" ng-model="vm.alipay_name" placeholder="支付宝实名认证姓名" required>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="rec2_FormBox ">
                            <div class="rec2_Title fl">
                                充值金额：
                            </div>
                            <div class="rec2_FomeContent fl">
                                <input type="text" class="inputText" value="\{{vm.pay_amount | currency:'':2}}" disabled>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="rec2_zfbText">
                            <p class="p01"><span>到账时间</span>&nbsp;如需马上到账或长时间未到账，可拨打客服电话：400-692-1388</p>
                            <p class="p02"> ·  08:30 - 20:30 （30分钟内到账）</p>
                            <p class="p02">·  20:30 以后     （次日09:00前到账）</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div ng-show="vm.alipayConfirm">
                        <div class="zfbBox jq_zfbBox" >
                            <div class="zfbLeft fl">
                                <div class="zfbText">
                                    <p>您的支付宝账户：<em class="fb">\{{vm.alipay_account}}</em></p>
                                    <p>您本次转账金额：<span class="color_f2991b">￥<span>\{{vm.pay_amount | currency:'':2}}</span></span></p>
                                </div>
                                <div class="zfbText2">
                                    <p class="color_c82217">用手机支付宝扫一扫</p>
                                    <p>快速转账，免手续费</p>
                                    <img src="/images/zfb_pay.jpg"/>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="zfbRight fl">
                                <div class="zfbText zfbText3 pr">
                                    <p>收款人支付宝账户：<em class="em01" id="zfbZh">chongzhi@niujinwang.com</em></p>
                                    <p>收款人账户名称：<em class="fb color_c82217">北京小牛普惠科技有限公司</em></p>
                                </div>
                                <div class="zfbText2">
                                    <p class="color_c82217">您还可以</p>
                                    <p>登录支付宝网站付款</p>
                                    <a href="https://shenghuo.alipay.com/send/payment/fill.htm" target="_blank"><img class="img01" src="/images/zfb2.jpg"/></a>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="rec2_yhBox  undis">
                    <div class="rec2_yhkText fl">
                        <div class="rec2_img fl"></div>
                        <div class="fl">转账汇款</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="rec2_hkTable fl">
                        <table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
                            <!--
                            <tr>
                                <td width="180"><img src="../images/yh/cbc.jpg"/></td>
                                <td>
                                    帐号：1109 1260 9510 501<br />
                                    户名：臣乾金融信息服务（上海）有限公司<br />
